This paper is about face modeling using a deep learning approach, specifically Deep Boltzmann Machines (DBM). The paper focuses on the application of this approach to face images and evaluates its performance in various tasks such as facial super-resolution, off-angle reconstruction, occlusion removal, and age estimation. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) are also possible sub-categories given the focus on deep learning and image processing.
